    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tanks used temporarily for containing fuel or another substance, usually liquid or gas rather than solid. The tanks are not intended to be linked to the equipment for which that fuel or other substance is intended.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
